Information

Rebels Ireland 1916 with Lyn and Dylan Ebenezer.

2016 marks the centenary of the Easter Rising in Ireland, a bloody battle which sparked the long journey towards Irish independence. Broadcasters Lyn Ebenezer and his son Dylan embark on a special journey to trace the history, where they meet some of the leading figures in the campaign for independence, including Gerry Adams.
